arm_group.description:
The intervention consists of the following:
mailing deprescribing educational materials to care partners and people living with dementia (PLWD);
dyads will receive a telehealth visit with a clinical pharmacist to discuss the benefits and harms of the patient's medications with the patient and care partner in the context of their goals and preferences;
pharmacist- primary care provider (PCP) communication in which the pharmacist provides tailored deprescribing recommendations to the PCP.
